commit.message: company: Rewrite -proof-goto-point for compatibility with ProofGeneral/PG#559
font-lock: Highlight (** comments in font-lock-doc-face

Revert "Support ProofGeneral/PG#559 + `C-u C-c C-RET` (#247)"

This reverts commit 9cef9d2933c531f7fa77348927137302579101b2.
It's not compatible with PG without ProofGeneral/PG#559.

Support ProofGeneral/PG#559 + `C-u C-c C-RET` (#247)

* Make company-coq compatible with PR https://github.com/ProofGeneral/PG/pull/559

To reproduce:
* Given company-coq
* and `Proof-General > Quick Options > Processing > Omit Proofs`,
* When doing `C-u C-c C-RET`,
* Then the considered lemmas should be fully processed.

commit.message:
features: Disable the spinner by default

Prompted by https://github.com/ProofGeneral/PG/issues/524

Change from :type imagemagick to :type png in company-coq-LaTeX

ImageMagick isn't included in the default Emacs build any more.
readme: Remove an outdated bit

Change current-buffer to proof-script-buffer in company-coq-library-path

Fixes GH-241.

Check the current buffer's name in jump-to-definition

Closes GH-238.
Combine our syntactic-face-function with others (don't overwrite them)
Only show the hello message once per Emacs session

Ignore neighboring [.,;] characters when deciding whether to prettify (#235)

This means that .->. now gets prettified as .→.
